{"tid":397902,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"失眠的你入一入黎","createTime":"2017-09-12T21:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T23:41:07.000Z","uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"591cf52817d546a025380ce44cf055165c69d571","tid":397902,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:05:41.000Z","msg":"晚晚都失眠到朝早7,8點先眼訓，但朝早要返學，夜晚又要返工，根本無精神聽書做野。係晚晚放工食完飯眼訓就最多訓3個鐘就醒，有時朝早無堂/走堂先可以訓耐啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好慘啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人可以救我，我諗我個生理時鐘壞左"},{"pid":"f95fbe80a52dd8c8e7f90fe17620dc36d482655b","tid":397902,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:11:00.000Z","msg":"救命啊屌"},{"pid":"8a4d4cad2615242eb304cb2ba32e511c93db5fc8","tid":397902,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救命啊屌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea818a5fdbbd9857f3f9f6d74c5a26a11302b4d8","tid":397902,"uid":135645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:42:48.000Z","msg":"我都係晚晚五點醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efd9265df19ae3f5b591f1411f91cf0476ac873","tid":397902,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係晚晚五點醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我2,3點醒。。你算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816e59741d6d1afaf0690003c6e715304b270c91","tid":397902,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T22:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65ac278dd0cc396e7af96665c73420abcc153a55","tid":397902,"uid":7466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T22:37:57.000Z","msg":"我以前都有段時間失眠過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我買左支伏特加 每晚訓之前就飲一至兩啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後未試過訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afc1c4b5f46e3a43899027d2f0fb25273f5a38a","tid":397902,"uid":140935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T23:41:07.000Z","msg":"Sleep at 11pm, like me"}]}